############################################################
# Body
############################################################

BEGIN_PGML
You bought a new car for [`[$bc]`] with a zero interest loan over a five-year period. That means you'll have to pay [`[$rc]`] each month for the next five years ([`60`] months) to pay it off. According to this information, the equation [`y=[$f]`] models the loan balance after [`x`] months, where [`y`] is in dollars. Make a graph of this equation.

[_]{$gt}{1}

END_PGML

############################################################
